Description.SourceString: The World Map is full of levels to complete, and serves as your main area of progression. Defeat the Stronghold in a region to unlock playing higher difficulties of levels in the region. Complete every level of a difficulty to get a bag of gems! Don't know which level to try next? The Play button will cycle through suggestions for different element levels.
